fr.zcraft.quartzlib.components.worker

Annotation Type WorkerAttributes


  • @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
 @Target(value=TYPE)
public @interface WorkerAttributes
    Defines various data about a given worker class.

    • Optional Element Summary

      Optional Elements 
      Modifier and Type Optional Element and Description
      String name
      Defines the name of the Worker.
      boolean queriesMainThread
      Defines if the Worker needs to query the main thread or not.

    • Element Detail

      • name

        public abstract String name
        Defines the name of the Worker. The named is used in various places, such as thread name or logging.
        Returns:
        The name of the worker.
        Default:
        ""

      • queriesMainThread

        public abstract boolean queriesMainThread
        Defines if the Worker needs to query the main thread or not. See the Worker class documentation for more information.
        Returns:
        If the Worker queries the main thread;
        Default:
        false
